{"data":{"page":{"id":"cddfd2e1-c790-5c53-813a-3ee29139cad8","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/gruposoledad/francia/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch France website</a>\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/gruposoledad/insaturbo/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch InsaTurbo intro</a>\n</p>\n<p>Grupo Soledad asked me to create a visually attractive website for the French market. They wanted to showcase their catalog of car tyres and batteries and be able to update the offers of the website using a simple CMS.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7654889251052ca1c961399ebc575945/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7654889251052ca1c961399ebc575945/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/7654889251052ca1c961399ebc575945/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/974fd51e60ae3ee92c6e42a4c1093f92/877ff/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/974fd51e60ae3ee92c6e42a4c1093f92/d2504/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/974fd51e60ae3ee92c6e42a4c1093f92/877ff/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>Grupo Soledad also asked me to build a multi-lingual animated Flash intro with navigation to use as a gateway to other websites from the group.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.099999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1fe27ee1369413493f43e78c7a2cfa0a/877ff/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1fe27ee1369413493f43e78c7a2cfa0a/d2504/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/1fe27ee1369413493f43e78c7a2cfa0a/877ff/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5e4d55e73b8a775d0d956b4d8492a330/877ff/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5e4d55e73b8a775d0d956b4d8492a330/d2504/4.jpg 500w,\n/static/5e4d55e73b8a775d0d956b4d8492a330/877ff/4.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>","fields":{"prefix":"4 December 2005"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Grupo Soledad","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/gruposoledad/","source":"work"}}